msgid "Welcome to vortem.ai!"
msgstr "Karibu kwa vortem.ai!"

msgid "Vortem.ai Setup Wizard"
msgstr "Mchawi wa Usanidi wa Vortem.ai"

msgid "Thank you for choosing vortem.ai Plugin. This wizard will help you set up your store quickly and easily."
msgstr "Asante kwa kuchagua programu jalizi ya vortem.ai. Mchawi huyu atakusaidia kusanidi duka lako haraka na kwa urahisi."

msgid "To use Vortem's product selling services, you need an AliExpress account. You can connect your account from Settings → Vortem Login → AliExpress Integration. If you don't have an account, you can sign up directly from there."
msgstr "Ili kutumia huduma za uuzaji wa bidhaa za Vortem, unahitaji akaunti ya AliExpress. Unaweza kuunganisha akaunti yako kutoka Mipangilio → Ingia Vortem → Ujumuishaji wa AliExpress. Ikiwa huna akaunti, unaweza kujisajili moja kwa moja kutoka huko."

msgid "To use Vortem's product selling services, you need an AliExpress account."
msgstr "Ili kutumia huduma za uuzaji wa bidhaa za Vortem, unahitaji akaunti ya AliExpress."

msgid "You can connect your account from Settings → Vortem Login → AliExpress Integration."
msgstr "Unaweza kuunganisha akaunti yako kutoka Mipangilio → Ingia Vortem → Ujumuishaji wa AliExpress."

msgid "If you don't have an account, you can sign up directly from there."
msgstr "Ikiwa huna akaunti, unaweza kujisajili moja kwa moja kutoka huko."

