msgid "Terms & Conditions"
msgstr "Vigezo na Masharti"

msgid "1. License Agreement"
msgstr "1. Makubaliano ya Leseni"

msgid "By using this plugin, you agree to comply with all applicable laws and regulations. The plugin is provided under the GPL v2 or later license."
msgstr "Kwa kutumia programu jalizi hii, unakubali kutii sheria na kanuni zote zinazotumika. Programu jalizi inatolewa chini ya leseni ya GPL v2 au ya baadaye."

msgid "Sign up"
msgstr "Jisajili"

msgid "Sign up to get started"
msgstr "Jisajili ili kuanza"

msgid "Congratulations! Your vortem.ai plugin has been successfully configured."
msgstr "Hongera! Programu jalizi yako ya vortem.ai imesanidiwa kikamilifu."

msgid "What's next?"
msgstr "Nini kinafuata?"

msgid "Need Help?"
msgstr "Unahitaji Msaada?"

msgid "Our support team is here to help you get started."
msgstr "Timu yetu ya usaidizi iko hapa kukusaidia kuanza."

msgid "Step %1$d of %2$d"
msgstr "Hatua ya %1$d kati ya %2$d"

msgid "I have read and agree to the %1$sTerms & Conditions%2$s"
msgstr "Nimesoma na kukubaliana na %1$sVigezo na Masharti%2$s"

msgid "vortem.ai Plugin Terms of Service"
msgstr "Masharti ya Huduma ya Programu Jalizi ya vortem.ai"

msgid "1. authentication Agreement"
msgstr "1. Makubaliano ya Uthibitishaji"

msgid "By using this plugin, you agree to comply with all applicable laws and regulations. The plugin is provided under the GPL v2 or later authentication."
msgstr "Kwa kutumia programu jalizi hii, unakubali kutii sheria na kanuni zote zinazotumika. Programu jalizi inatolewa chini ya uthibitishaji wa GPL v2 au wa baadaye."

msgid "2. Data Usage"
msgstr "2. Matumizi ya Data"

msgid "We collect and process data necessary for the operation of the service, including product information, order details, and customer data. All data is handled in accordance with our privacy policy."
msgstr "Tunakusanya na kuchakata data muhimu kwa uendeshaji wa huduma, ikijumuisha maelezo ya bidhaa, maelezo ya oda, na data ya mteja. Data yote inashughulikiwa kwa mujibu wa sera yetu ya faragha."

msgid "3. Service Availability"
msgstr "3. Upatikanaji wa Huduma"

msgid "While we strive to maintain high service availability, we cannot guarantee uninterrupted service. We reserve the right to perform maintenance and updates as needed."
msgstr "Ingawa tunajitahidi kudumisha upatikanaji wa huduma wa hali ya juu, hatuwezi kuhakikisha huduma isiyo na katiziko. Tunahifadhi haki ya kufanya ukarabati na masasisho inapo hitajika."

msgid "4. Support"
msgstr "4. Usaidizi"

msgid "Technical support is provided through our support channels. Response times may vary based on the complexity of the issue."
msgstr "Usaidizi wa kiufundi unatolewa kupitia njia zetu za usaidizi. Muda wa kujibu unaweza kutofautiana kulingana na utata wa suala husika."

msgid "5. Updates"
msgstr "5. Masasisho"

msgid "Plugin updates are provided to improve functionality and security. It is recommended to keep the plugin updated to the latest version."
msgstr "Masasisho ya programu jalizi yanatolewa ili kuboresha utendakazi na usalama. Inapendekezwa kusasisha programu jalizi hadi toleo la hivi punde."

msgid "Enter your Vortem.ai authentication key to activate the plugin and access all features."
msgstr "Weka ufunguo wako wa uthibitishaji wa Vortem.ai ili kuwezesha programu jalizi na kufikia vipengele vyote."

msgid "You can find your authentication key in your Vortem.ai account dashboard."
msgstr "Unaweza kupata ufunguo wako wa uthibitishaji kwenye dashibodi ya akaunti yako ya Vortem.ai."

msgid "Need help?"
msgstr "Unahitaji msaada?"

msgid "Complete the setup wizard to configure your authentication and get started."
msgstr "Kamilisha mchawi wa usanidi ili kusanidi uthibitishaji wako na kuanza."

