msgid "You agree to be bound by these terms."
msgstr "Unakubali kufungwa na masharti haya."

msgid "I consent to data processing"
msgstr "Ninaridhia usindikaji wa data"

msgid "I understand and agree that this plugin sends my site data (site URL, WordPress version, plugin version, currency preference, WooCommerce product data when importing products, order shipping information when processing orders, and plugin/theme metadata when using security features) to vortem.ai servers (https://c.vortem.ai) for processing, analytics, and service delivery. No data is sent before you provide explicit consent, and the plugin remains functional if you decline (features that depend on vortem.ai will simply be unavailable). Sending an inventory of installed plugins/themes for vulnerability lookup follows the same pattern used by Wordfence, Patchstack, WPScan, and Jetpack Protect."
msgstr "Naelewa na nakubali kuwa programu-jalizi hii inatuma data ya wavuti yangu (URL ya tovuti, toleo la WordPress, toleo la programu-jalizi, mapendeleo ya sarafu, data ya bidhaa za WooExpress wakati wa kuagiza, maelezo ya usafirishaji wakati wa kusindika maagizo, na metadata ya programu-jalizi/mandhari wakati wa kutumia vipengele vya usalama) kwa seva za vortem.ai (https://c.vortem.ai) kwa usindikaji, uchanganuzi na utoaji huduma. Hakuna data inayotumwa kabla ya ridhaa yako wazi, na programu-jalizi bado inafanya kama ukikataa (vipengele vinavyotegemea vortem.ai havitapatikana). Kutuma orodha ya programu-jalizi/mandhari yaliyosakinishwa kutafuta mapungufu kufuata mfano ule ule wa Wordfence, Patchstack, WPScan na Jetpack Protect."

